# MADA — EmailJS configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This project uses EmailJS for client-side email delivery
# (pure static site, no backend required).
#
# Steps:
#   1. Create a free account at https://emailjs.com
#   2. Add a Service (Gmail, SMTP, Outlook…)
#   3. Create a Template — subject and body should reference:
#        {{from_name}} {{phone}} {{from_email}}
#        {{company}}   {{message}} {{date}}
#   4. Copy the values below and paste them into site/modal.js
#      (EMAILJS_KEY, EMAILJS_SVC, EMAILJS_TPL constants at the top)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
CONTACT_EMAIL=contact@mada.ma
